+  {
+    ...CITY,
+    title: "Castles, Libraries and Curiosities: Prague's Cultural Vaults",
+    topic: "Museums",
+    description:
+      "Prague's museums hide in plain sight — a castle complex spanning a millennium, baroque libraries too beautiful for browsing, and the Jewish Quarter's layered testimony. The cultural circuit with queue strategy for Europe's most compressed historic core.",
